race.comment: PRINCE OF SYNERGY (5) has been nudged out here her last two over 1400m. The mile shouldn't be an issue and she maps for the run of the race. SARAH'S SONNETS (12) is ready for the step-up in trip. Didn't have much luck at Ballina last time when well-supported and she carries 2kg less in this. A winning chance. ROYAL EDITION (6) also presents third-up and he led and just missed at Toowoomba when she last tackled this trip. Has a wide gate but gets KWT and is ready to fire. JAMCART (2) has an awkward gate as well but is a likely improver from the in-form Munce yard. IN AND AWAY (1) comes back in trip and may be the best of the rest.
